query:
SELECT
    q.ranges AS "period!: DateRange",
    COALESCE(SUM(h.total_living_weight), 0.0)::DOUBLE PRECISION AS "weight!"
FROM
    hauls h
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT
            unnest(range_agg(period)) AS ranges
        FROM
            hauls h
        WHERE
            h.fiskeridir_vessel_id = $1
           AND h.period <@ $2::tstzrange
    ) q ON q.ranges <@ h.period
WHERE
    h.fiskeridir_vessel_id = $1
    AND h.period <@ $2::tstzrange
GROUP BY
    q.ranges
